747
00:32:22,110 --> 00:32:23,000
Memang benar

748
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:25,020
Membunuh dua burung dengan satu batu.

749
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,030
Benchang,

750
00:32:27,310 --> 00:32:29,270
Anda harus segera mengambil keputusan.

751
