kayu pinus itu sendiri.

778
00:34:02,790 --> 00:34:03,720
Manajer Zhen,

779
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:06,110
Metode Anda sungguh brilian.

780
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:07,730
Entah itu jelaga

781
00:34:07,790 --> 00:34:09,070
