805
00:35:03,590 --> 00:35:04,190
Jingdong.

806
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:06,930
Guru, Anda terlalu serius.

807
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:09,670
Anda dan Manajer Zhen telah memikirkan semuanya
