905
00:40:11,030 --> 00:40:12,630
Izinkan saya memperjelasnya hari ini.

906
00:40:13,110 --> 00:40:13,880
Li Zhen,

907
00:40:14,510 --> 00:40:16,190
Aku sama sekali tidak mempercayaimu,

908
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:18,880
