mengambil alih Li Ink.

909
00:40:18,880 --> 00:40:19,880
Tian Jiangyue.

910
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:22,010
Kamu berbicara tanpa berpikir.

911
00:40:22,400 --> 00:40:24,630
